headline: This 5.5%-Yielding Dividend Stock's Smart Strategy Continues to Drive Growth
summary: The REIT routinely brings on new partners.  Vici Properties (NYSE: VICI) has grown faster than its peers over the years.  The real estate investment trust (REIT) has raised its dividend payment at a 7% compound annual rate since its formation more than seven years ago.
